body:
  {
    "status": "Success",
    "results": [

  {
            "patient_id": "P001",
            "redacted_text": "Dr [NAME] in the respiratory clinic was absolutely wonderful. She took time to explain my COPD management plan and made sure I understood every step. The nurse on reception, [NAME], was also very welcoming.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "P002",
            "redacted_text": "The parking at [ADDRESS] is very limited. I had to walk from the Westfield car park which is difficult at my age.",
            "entity_count": 1
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "P003",
            "redacted_text": "I had my appointment on [DATE_TIME] at [DATE_TIME] and wasn't seen until after [DATE_TIME]. Dr [NAME] seemed rushed and didn't listen to my concerns about the medication side effects. I called the clinic at [PHONE] twice before my appointment to ask about preparation and nobody answered. My wife [NAME] had a much better experience at the Chermside Day Surgery last month.",
            "entity_count": 6
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p004",
            "redacted_text": "The physiotherapist [NAME] was great. He gave me a detailed home exercise program after my knee surgery and followed up via email at [EMAIL] to check on my progress. Very impressed with that level of care.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p005",
            "redacted_text": "The online booking system could be easier to use. I ended up calling reception to book because I couldn't figure out the Zedoc portal. I was referred by Dr [NAME] at the Ipswich Hospital and the transition was smooth.",
            "entity_count": 1
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p006",
            "redacted_text": "Nurse [NAME] in the diabetes clinic was exceptional. She spent over 40 minutes with me going through my HbA1c results and adjusting my insulin plan. She also coordinated with my GP Dr [NAME] at the Toowoomba Medical Practice to ensure consistent care.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p007",
            "redacted_text": "Dr [NAME] is always thorough and patient. She remembers details from previous visits which makes me feel valued.",
            "entity_count": 1
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p008",
            "redacted_text": "I'm [AGE] old and find the forms quite difficult to fill in. My daughter [NAME] usually helps me but she wasn't available this time. Could you offer some assistance at the front desk for elderly patients? Also my Medicare number is [UK_NATIONAL_HEALTH_SERVICE_NUMBER] and I think there was a billing error on my last visit on [DATE_TIME].",
            "entity_count": 4
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p009",
            "redacted_text": "The midwifery team, especially [NAME] and [NAME], were amazing throughout my pregnancy. They made me feel safe and supported. The antenatal classes at the centre on [ADDRESS] were also excellent.",
            "entity_count": 3
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0010",
            "redacted_text": "It would be nice to have later appointment slots. As a working mum I find it hard to attend before [DATE_TIME]. My employer at Bright Horizons Childcare is not always flexible with time off. I recommended this clinic to my sister-in-law [NAME] who is expecting in July.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0011",
            "redacted_text": "The new blood collection nurse, [NAME], was very skilled. Best blood draw I've had - barely felt it. He mentioned he previously worked at the Royal Brisbane and Women's Hospital.",
            "entity_count": 1
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0012",
            "redacted_text": "The results portal is confusing. I had to call Dr [NAME]'s office at [PHONE] to get my pathology explained because I couldn't understand the online report.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0013",
            "redacted_text": "Dr [NAME] and Nurse [NAME] were both excellent. They were respectful of my cultural needs and ensured a female practitioner was available for my examination. This was very important to me.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0014",
            "redacted_text": "The interpreter service was not available on [DATE_TIME] when my mother attended. She speaks Arabic and struggled to communicate her symptoms. Please ensure interpreters are booked in advance. My mother [NAME] (patient ID PAT-91603) would like to provide feedback separately. Can someone contact her at [EMAIL] to arrange an Arabic-language survey?",
            "entity_count": 3
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0015",
            "redacted_text": "Outstanding mental health support from psychologist Dr [NAME]. She helped me develop coping strategies after my workplace incident at BHP Mitsubishi Alliance in [ADDRESS] last year. The telehealth option made it possible to continue sessions when I was FIFO.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0016",
            "redacted_text": "The mental health waiting list is too long. I was referred on [DATE_TIME] and didn't get my first appointment until [DATE_TIME]. That's nearly 8 weeks.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0017",
            "redacted_text": "The wound care nurse [NAME] was thorough and gentle. She explained the healing process for my post-surgical wound clearly and gave me written instructions to take home.",
            "entity_count": 1
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0018",
            "redacted_text": "I received a reminder SMS from Zedoc to complete this survey but the link didn't work on my Samsung phone. I had to use my husband [NAME]'s iPhone instead. The SMS came from number [PHONE]. I was transferred from Logan Hospital after my surgery there on [DATE_TIME]. The handover between hospitals could have been smoother - my medication list wasn't updated correctly.",
            "entity_count": 3
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0019",
            "redacted_text": "The entire cardiology team is first-rate. Dr [NAME] personally called me at home on [PHONE] to discuss my stress test results. That kind of proactive communication is rare and very reassuring.",
            "entity_count": 2
        },

  {
            "patient_id": "p0020",
            "redacted_text": "The car park needs more disabled bays. I have a temporary mobility permit after my cardiac rehab and struggled to find a spot on [DATE_TIME]. My cardiologist at the Prince Charles Hospital, Dr [NAME], also coordinates with Dr [NAME] here which gives me great confidence in my care plan.",
            "entity_count": 3
        }
    ],
    "errors": []
}
